BitTorrent Simulator

A BitTorrent simulator used to test different algorithms.

BUILDING

  ant

RUNNING

  eport CLASSPATH=/paths/to/third-party/jars:/path/to/build/output
  java edu.ualr.bittorrent.Experiment

DEPENDENCIES

 - Google Java Collections Library [http://code.google.com/p/google-collections/]
 - Apache log4j [http://logging.apache.org/log4j/index.html]
 - Apache Ant [http://ant.apache.org/]
 - Joda-Time [http://joda-time.sourceforge.net/]
 - Google Guice [http://code.google.com/p/google-guice]

